N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 153.4 - Licensing period

State Regulations

The annual licensing period as provided for by section 146
of the law shall be the calendar year. All licenses issued during each license
period shall expire on December 31 of that year. Notes
